libwmf 0.2.15

Upstream: https://github.com/caolanm/libwmf
Revision: 94b932de7a4aa6bceb0ff630c65b4aa9cc1dfd1e
License: LGPL-2.0-or-later; bundled Nimbus fonts carry their own license.

KiCad builds only the WMF parser and GD raster backend needed by the OrCAD
importer. Upstream converters, command-line tools, and unused output backends
are not built.

Local changes:
- Disable libwmf's Windows DLL entry point, relocation helpers, and import/export
  annotations for the static KiCad target.  KiCad supplies the installed font
  directory explicitly.
